"Two-factor authentication will be required in %(days)s day(s). Please set up "
"2FA in your account settings to continue accessing the admin."
msgstr ""
"Autentikasi dua faktor akan diperlukan dalam %(days)s hari. Silakan atur 2FA "
"di pengaturan akun Anda untuk terus mengakses admin."

