"Two-factor authentication is required for admin access. Please set up 2FA to "
"continue."
msgstr ""
"Autentikasi dua faktor diperlukan untuk akses admin. Silakan atur 2FA untuk "
"melanjutkan."

msgid "Whether this object has been soft deleted"
