msgstr "Dokumentasi API eCommerce Spwig"

msgid ""
"## Spwig API Documentation\n"
"\n"
"Welcome to the Spwig eCommerce Platform API documentation. This API enables "
"you to build custom headless storefronts, mobile apps, and integrations.\n"
"\n"
"### Authentication\n"
"\n"
"Most endpoints require authentication using one of these methods:\n"
"\n"
"- **Token Authentication**: Include `Authorization: Token <your-token>` "
"header\n"
"- **Session Authentication**: Use Spwig session cookies (for browser-based "
"apps)\n"
"\n"
"Public endpoints (like product catalog) allow anonymous access.\n"
"\n"
"### API Standards\n"
"\n"
"- **Pagination**: List endpoints return 20 items per page by default. Use `?"
"page=N` to navigate.\n"
"- **Filtering**: Most list endpoints support query parameter filtering\n"
"- **Multi-language**: Set `Accept-Language` header for localized responses\n"
"- **Multi-currency**: Currency information included in price responses\n"
"\n"
"### Response Format\n"
"\n"
"All endpoints return JSON with a consistent format:\n"
"```json\n"
"{\n"
"  \"success\": true,\n"
"  \"data\": { ... },\n"
"  \"message\": \"Optional status message\"\n"
"}\n"
"```\n"
"\n"
"### Rate Limiting\n"
"\n"
"Public endpoints may be rate-limited. Authenticated requests have higher "
"limits."
msgstr ""
"## Dokumentasi API Spwig Selamat datang di dokumentasi API Platform "
"eCommerce Spwig. API ini memungkinkan Anda untuk membangun toko online "
"headless kustom, aplikasi mobile, dan integrasi. ### Autentikasi Sebagian "
"besar endpoint memerlukan autentikasi menggunakan salah satu metode berikut: "
"- **Autentikasi Token**: Sertakan header `Authorization: Token <your-token>` "
"- **Autentikasi Sesi**: Gunakan cookie sesi Spwig (untuk aplikasi berbasis "
"browser) Endpoint publik (seperti katalog produk) memungkinkan akses anonim. "
"### Standar API - **Paginasi**: Endpoint daftar mengembalikan 20 item per "
"halaman secara default. Gunakan `?page=N` untuk navigasi. - **Penyaringan**: "
"Sebagian besar endpoint daftar mendukung penyaringan parameter query - "
"**Multi-bahasa**: Tetapkan header `Accept-Language` untuk respons berbahasa "
"lokal - **Multi-mata uang**: Informasi mata uang termasuk dalam respons "
"harga ### Format Respons Semua endpoint mengembalikan JSON dengan format "
"yang konsisten: ```json {\n"
"  \"success\": true,\n"
"  \"data\": { ... },\n"
"  \"message\": \"Optional status message\"\n"
"} ``` ### Batas Tingkat Penggunaan Endpoint publik mungkin dibatasi tingkat "
"penggunaannya. Permintaan yang terautentikasi memiliki batas yang lebih "
"tinggi."

